Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Freeze-Dried Fruits Market

Freeze-dried fruits market is expected to grow at a growth rate of 9.00% in the forecast period 2021 to 2028. The rapid rise in consumption rate of natural ingredients in various emerging economies is the factor for the freeze-dried fruits market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

The major growing factor towards freeze dried fruit market is the exceptional shelf life of the product with no added preservative to store for a long duration at home. The increased shelf-life makes freeze dried fruit as a profitable product during its supply chain which is heightening the overall demand for freeze-dried fruits market over the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Also the market is driven by the busy lifestyle of people is demanding healthy, and convenience foods like freeze dried fruits as well as the high nutritional value of these fruits. Increasing disposable income, growing rapidly growing population across the world, penetration of different retail formats along with the change in lifestyle leading to high demand for consumption of freeze-dried fruits, rising trend toward vegan diets and the increase in demand for packaged food items are fueling the demand for freeze-dried fruits market. However, the freeze drying equipments are relatively costlier than other dryers and the accessibility of other drying techniques such as spray drying, infused drying and others have low operational cost when compared to freeze drying technique, which is projected to act as a restraint towards the growth of freeze-dried fruit market. Furthermore, the demand by the different types of processed foods that use freeze dried fruit has also increased, which is also shedding a positive growth towards the freeze-dried fruit market.

Furthermore, growing demand for convenience food, changing lifestyles as well as the untapped potential in the developing countries are also expected to fuel the market growth. Moreover, as rapid developments in the global packaged food industry and various advantages coupled with the fresh fruits will further generate new opportunities for the freeze-dried fruits market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. But, the lack of awareness and high cost coupled with the product manufacturing will pose as a market challenges for freeze-dried fruits in the above mentioned forecast period.

